{"tid":1984485,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大學生包圍警總塗鴉「condom」認罪候判","createTime":"2020-04-22T13:04:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-22T15:09:33.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e8e68abc08e5ac892c360141396ef65267070251","tid":1984485,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T13:04:53.000Z","msg":"大學生包圍警總塗鴉認罪候判<br />\n22.04.2020 20:52<br />\n<br />\n一名大學生去年6月21日包圍警察總部示威期間，用白色油漆在警總外牆塗鴉，下午在東區裁判法院承認刑事毀壞罪，裁判官押後至下月20日判刑，索取被告的感化報告。<br />\n<br />\n案情指，19歲男被告王愷銘當日以白色油漆，在警總外牆寫上安全套的英語「condom」等字眼，約一個月後被捕，警誡下承認塗鴉，諷刺警方被用完即棄。辯方求情指，被告是傳播系二年級生，日後有意從事新聞工作，因想表達自己想法才犯案，認罪是為自己的行為負責，亦願意賠償1200元清潔費，希望法庭判以罰款。裁判官指不適宜罰款，先索取感化報告。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1282672&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1282672%26csid%3D261_341&d=uNNx3RetO4MSseDCYlD6CslSugA1I0CCabXjLbCjl00%3D&h=f6c749c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1282672&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"a678796a1113ed3f630b559fdc3b74536819da70","tid":1984485,"uid":73959,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T13:09:39.000Z","msg":"裁判官指不適宜罰款？<br />\n唔罰又想點呀？傷牆罪呀？"},{"pid":"59814eff6eb9b6b90682b499ce5591e892d10bb5","tid":1984485,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a678796a1113ed3f630b559fdc3b74536819da70","tid":1984485,"uid":73959,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T13:09:39.000Z","msg":"裁判官指不適宜罰款？<br />\n唔罰又想點呀？傷牆罪呀？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T13:16:23.000Z","msg":"可以係感化令/社會服務令"},{"pid":"7f95d1b29a0640c863545ae44b1a737c920c3d1b","tid":1984485,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T13:17:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g35Yum7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg35Yum7.jpg&h=bb2